StarFlier:

"So when can I meet Hydras? Sounds like there are only 3 dragons here 
on so far. Perhaps others will arrive later on."

She transformed into bot mode.  But instead of an insignia, there was 
the pic of a dragon. "I'm from the Dracobots.  From Compositron. 
Small planet on the other side of the galaxy from old Cybertron. 
Which planet are you from?"
She looked around the old ship. "Perhaps we should get going. May I 
join you and your group? You mentioned a boss. So I assume there is 
more bots somewhere. Am I right?"
